<div class="faq-sec padd-t-b-100 pt-greenbg">
   <div class="container">
      <div class="heading-1">
         <h2>FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="question-col pt-faq-sec">
         <div id="accordion-2" class="accordion accordion-sec">
            <div class="card ">
               <div class="card-header collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#d1">
                  <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="card-title">
                  When should I start drinking Mira’s Pregnancy Tea?
                  </a>
               </div>
               <div id="d1" class="card-body collapse" data-parent="#accordion" >
                  <div class="accordion-link-col">
                     <p class="description">You can start drinking Mira’s Pregnancy tea starting from your first trimester. We recommend not to drink more than 2 tea servings per day.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
               <div class="card-header collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#d2">
                  <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="card-title">
                  How do I brew it?
                  </a>
               </div>
               <div id="d2" class="card-body collapse" data-parent="#accordion" >
                  <div class="accordion-link-col">
                     <p class="description">Pop one of Mira’s Pregnancy Tea bags into your mug, pour over boiling water and stir. Wait two minutes for the best taste. Enjoy! Due to the peeling of our natural ingredients, you may see sediments releasing during brewing.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
               <div class="card-header collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#d3">
                  <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="card-title">
                  How do I store Mira’s Pregnancy Tea?
                  </a>
               </div>
               <div id="d3" class="card-body collapse" data-parent="#accordion" >
                  <div class="accordion-link-col">
                     <p class="description">Store in a dry place at room temperature. Fasten the zipper after opening.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
         </div>
      </div>
